sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant FastAPI
    participant Celery
    participant Redis
    
    Client->>FastAPI: POST /batch/ingest (file_list)
    FastAPI->>Celery: Create batch job
    Celery->>Redis: Track job progress
    loop For each file
        Celery->>Celery: Process individual file
    end
    Celery->>Redis: Update job status
    Client->>FastAPI: GET /batch/status (job_id)
    FastAPI->>Redis: Get job progress
    FastAPI->>Client: Return status/results